Fully compactible with TESV.exe version 1.3.10.0


v1
- Fixed some error points from ini
-added lines, and disabled some things thats not needed
-tweak for best performance

This will increase your fps, if it doesn\'t then check your settings. This is just tweaked skyrim ini not just the ones you see when you search how to fix skyrim lag. if you do not trust me test it and if you think it doest work then delete it it will create another one.Or make a backup





Recommended Mod-
Skybooster

Make sure you DO NOT set the graphices level to ultra or high only medium,
Meaning when you click skyrim launcher(to Run skyrim) you will see low,medium,high
and ultra


And i will add and tweak the medium ini to have better performance and im working on that now

This is compatible with all Nvidia Cards and ATI radeon Cards
